                <ul>
                    <li>Architected and implemented scalable microservices using .NET Core and Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS).</li>
                    <li>Optimized application performance by integrating Azure App Services and Azure Functions.</li>
                    <li>Developed CI/CD pipelines for automated deployments on Azure DevOps.</li>
                </ul>
