                    <li>Collaborated with the QA team to improve test coverage and reduce defects by 20%.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
            <div class="content">
                <p><strong>Master's in Computer Science</strong> - University of Technology, 2007</p>
                <p><strong>Bachelor's in Information Technology</strong> - College of Engineering, 2005</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="section-title">Certifications</h2>
            <div class="content">
                <ul>
                    <li>Microsoft Certified: Azure Solutions Architect Expert</li>
                    <li>Microsoft Certified: Azure Developer Associate</li>
                    <li>Scrum Alliance Certified ScrumMaster (CSM)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>
            <div class="content">
                <p>Email: johndoe@example.com</p>
                <p>Phone: +1 (123) 456-7890</p>
                <a href="#" class="contact-btn">Download Resume</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 John Doe. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
